window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A gripping horror thriller that will leave you wanting more. Start listening to the first book in this dark and captivating re-imagined series of the classic story of <i>Hansel and Gretel</i>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>There is an ancient evil in the Back Country, dormant for centuries but now hungry and lurking.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>When it sets its sights on an unsuspecting mother one routine morning along an isolated stretch of highway, a quiet farming family is suddenly thrust into a world of unspeakable terror, and young Gretel must learn to be a hero.</p>"; 
